---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<section class='py-24 relative'>
  <!-- Decorative geometric shapes in Bauhaus style -->
  <div class='absolute left-0 top-0 w-32 h-32 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2'>
    <div class='w-full h-full border-8 border-accent-red rotate-45'></div>
  </div>
  <div class='absolute right-0 bottom-0 w-24 h-24 translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2'>
    <div class='w-full h-full bg-accent-blue rounded-full opacity-20'></div>
  </div>

  <div class='container relative'>
    <div class='max-w-4xl mx-auto'>
      <!-- Section Title with Bauhaus-inspired typography -->
      <h2 class='text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-12 tracking-tight text-center'>Philosophy & Vision</h2>

      <!-- Three-column values layout -->
      <div class='grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16'>
        <div class='space-y-4'>
          <h3 class='text-xl font-bold'>Creative Innovation</h3>
          <p class='text-gray-600'>Merging technical precision with artistic vision to craft unique digital experiences that resonate and inspire.</p>
        </div>
        <div class='space-y-4'>
          <h3 class='text-xl font-bold'>Cross-Domain Mastery</h3>
          <p class='text-gray-600'>Bridging software engineering, music composition, and storytelling to create harmonious, multi-dimensional solutions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class='space-y-4'>
          <h3 class='text-xl font-bold'>Cultural Impact</h3>
          <p class='text-gray-600'>Building experiences that contribute meaningfully to digital culture while pushing creative boundaries.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Personal statement with dynamic highlight -->
      <div class='relative bg-gray-50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-sm'>
        <div class='max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6'>
          <p class='text-lg'>
            I'm driven by the intersection of logic and creativity, where elegant code meets compelling storytelling. My work spans multiple disciplines because
            I believe the most innovative solutions emerge when we bridge different worlds.
          </p>
          <p class='text-lg'>
            Whether I'm architecting software systems, composing music, or crafting narratives, I approach each project with both technical rigor and creative
            intuition. This dual perspective allows me to create experiences that are not just functional, but meaningful and memorable.
          </p>
          <div class='text-lg font-medium pt-4'>â€” Javier Godoy (@gaulatti)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Bauhaus-inspired decorative elements animation */
  .rotate-45 {
    animation: gentleRotate 20s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes gentleRotate {
    from {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }
    to {
      transform: rotate(405deg);
    }
  }
</style>
